OL,3,CThousands raised for funeral of 'blue-
OL,4,Ceyed boy' who died in river
OL,6,FThe family of a 12-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fdied after getting into difficulty
OL,8,Fwhile swimming in a river are raising
OL,9,Fmoney to help "give him the beautiful
OL,10,Fsend-off he deserves."
OL,12,FJunior Slater, from Clayton-le-Woods,
OL,13,Flost his life in the River Ribble at
OL,14,FRibchester, Lancashire, on Tuesday, 26
OL,15,FMay, during a period of record-
OL,16,Fbreaking heat across the UK.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
