OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780074357
OL,3,CThousands raised for funeral of 'blue-
OL,4,Ceyed boy' who died in river
OL,6,FEmergency services, including police
OL,7,Funderwater search units and fire and
OL,8,Frescue crews, launched a large-scale
OL,9,Fsearch operation after concerns were
OL,10,Fraised for a boy swimming with friends.
OL,12,FThe child's body was recovered from
OL,13,Fthe water later that evening.
OL,15,FHis family has now set up a GoFundMe
OL,16,Fpage to give him the "beautiful send-
OL,17,Foff he deserves".
OL,19,FThey wrote: "Our hearts are completely
OL,20,Fbroken after tragically losing our
OL,21,Fbeautiful 12-year-old brother.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780074357
OL,3,CThousands raised for funeral of 'blue-
OL,4,Ceyed boy' who died in river
OL,6,F"He was the happiest, cheekiest soul,
OL,7,Falways making everyone laugh and
OL,8,Flighting up every room he walked into.
OL,10,F"He was a loving son, amazing little
OL,11,Fbrother, and the best uncle. He was
OL,12,Floved by so many people, and we were
OL,13,Fall so proud of him."
OL,15,FThey added: "We are raising money to
OL,16,Fhelp give him the beautiful send-off
OL,17,Fhe deserves and support our mum and
OL,18,Ffamily through this heartbreaking
OL,19,Ftime. Any donation or share would mean
OL,20,Fthe world to us.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
