OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780074357
OL,3,CThousands raised for funeral of 'blue-
OL,4,Ceyed boy' who died in river
OL,6,F"Forever 12. Forever loved."
OL,8,FIn a separate tribute released through
OL,9,FLancashire Police, his family
OL,10,Fdescribed Junior as their "little blue-
OL,11,Feyed boy" and the "life and soul of
OL,12,Four lives."
OL,14,FThe fundraiser has seen an outpouring
OL,15,Fof community support, reaching over
OL,16,F#11,000 of its #15,000 target within
OL,17,Fjust days, with over 400 people
OL,18,Fdonating.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
