OL,3,CThousands raised for funeral of 'blue-
OL,4,Ceyed boy' who died in river
OL,6,FJunior is one of 11 people, including
OL,7,Fseveral children, who have died in
OL,8,Fopen water across the UK over the past
OL,9,Fweek as temperatures soared.
OL,11,FThe spike in tragedies has prompted
OL,12,Femergency services and the Royal Life
OL,13,FSaving Society (RLSS) to reissue
OL,14,Furgent water safety warnings.
OL,16,FExperts have reminded the public that
OL,17,Fdespite hot air temperatures, open
OL,18,Fwater in rivers and lakes remains
OL,19,Fdangerously cold, increasing the risk
OL,20,Fof cold water shock.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
